        "creation_date": 1459874292,
        "body": "<p>Create your own <code>ResponseUtils<\/code> with the method<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public void write(PageContext pageContext, String text)\n        throws JspException {\n\n    JspWriter writer = pageContext.getOut();\n\n    try {\n        writer.print(text);\n\n    } catch (IOException e) {\n        throw new JspException(e);\n    }\n\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
